{
  "__comments": [
    "=================================================================",
    "Docker Engine Metrics Dashboard - Enhanced",
    "=================================================================",
    "",
    "REQUIRED METRICS (from Docker Engine API - exposed via /metrics):",
    "- engine_daemon_container_states_containers : Container states (running, paused, stopped)",
    "- engine_daemon_container_actions_seconds_* : Container action durations",
    "- engine_daemon_health_checks_total : Total health checks performed",
    "- engine_daemon_health_checks_failed_total : Failed health checks",
    "- engine_daemon_events_total : Total Docker events",
    "- engine_daemon_image_actions_seconds_* : Image operations",
    "- engine_daemon_network_actions_seconds_* : Network operations",
    "- engine_daemon_engine_cpus_cpus : CPU allocation",
    "- engine_daemon_engine_memory_bytes : Memory allocation",
    "",
    "FEATURES:",
    "- Per-LXC container breakdown with color coding",
    "- Real-time metrics and rates",
    "- Resource allocation tracking",
    "- Health check monitoring",
    "- Action timing analysis",
    "================================================================="
  ],
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
